<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.8.2">
<l>maṇimāmai kuṟaivillā malarmāta ruṟaimārpa</l>
<l>ṉaṇimāṉat taṭavaraittō ḷaṭalāḻit taṭakkaiyaṉ</l>
<l>paṇimāṉam piḻaiyāmē yaṭiyēṉaip paṇikoṇṭa</l>
<l>maṇimāyaṉ kavarāta maṭaneñcāṟ kuṟaivilamē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Except  the want for [our] sapphire darkness, without failing in humble attitude</l>
<l>towards him whose broad hand [holds] the deadly discus, with broad mountain shoulders</l>
<l>that are like ornaments on him on whose chest the flower woman dwells, we have no want for</l>
<l>[our] foolish heart that is not seized by the sapphire-dark one who has taken me into [his] service.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
